name: Virgo
description:
Being perfectionists, Virgos are very analytical, hardworking, and detail-oriented. They prefer organized life and practicality in everyday situations. Virgo, in another name the disappointed goddess, is known for their kindness and loyalty. Their strong belief in the goodness of humankind is the mission of their life.

Element: Earth
Quality: Mutable
Duality: Receptive
